      "m0:latentHeat": "Heat of fusion L_fus (J/mol) absorbed or released at constant T",
      "m0:clausiusClapeyron": "dP/dT = L_fus / (T * Delta_V_fus)",
      "m0:signature": "Latent heat plateau in heating/cooling curve; volume discontinuity",
      "m0:symmetryBreaking": "YES (Freezing direction) — spontaneous descent from continuous translational symmetry (liquid) to discrete lattice symmetry (crystal). Primary physical instance of SymmetryBreaking M2 candidate.",
