      "m0:latentHeat": "Heat of vaporization L_vap (J/mol); typically 5-10x L_fus",
      "m0:clausiusClapeyron": "dP/dT = L_vap / (T * Delta_V_vap) approx L_vap * P / (R * T^2)",
      "m0:idealGasLink": "Vapor pressure: ln(P) = -L_vap/(R*T) + const",
